- Required packages: scim scim-libs scim-tables
- Optional package: scim-bridge

- Install required packages for Fedora 5,6,7 (you must have an Internet Connection): 
	yum -y install scim scim-libs scim-tables scim-bridge
- Install required packages for Ubuntu 7 (you must have an Internet Connection): 
	sudo apt-get install scim-bridge scim-qtimm

To install, login as root and type:
	tar -zxf scim-tables-vietnamese-ext*.tar.gz
	cd scim-tables-vietnamese-ext/
	make install

To active scim:
- Fedora: go to System => Preference => [Personal =>] Input Method, select custom input method, then scim.
- Ubuntu: open terminal and type:
	im-switch -z en_US -s scim
See https://help.ubuntu.com/community/SCIM for detail.

Logout and relogin X session.

